                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi>.** <hi rend="italic">of unlawfully wounding.</hi>
                  </rs> Aged 36.—<hi rend="italic">He received a good character, but the prosecutor stated that he had been in custody several times for assaulting the police.—
